data.description: This 4-bed, 3.5-bath home in the heart of Fort Ben is waiting for you! The home offers an inviting office space with built-in speakers on the main floor, along with an open-concept design that seamlessly connects the family room, kitchen, and dining area. The kitchen features a granite-topped island, updated appliances, farmhouse sink, and pantry. Upstairs, find 4 bedrooms, including a primary suite w/ a full shower stall, double vanity, and walk-in closet. Two more full bathrooms serve the remaining bedrooms, alongside a convenient laundry/utility room. Relax on the screened in porch, or outside in the fenced in brick patio. Just minutes away from Fort Harrison State Park, The Fort Golf Course, dining options, fitness centers, and schools!
